This is a modified for GlassFish and Eclipse 3.6 plugin that allows headless build of our GlassFish plugins.
Original project is under http://code.google.com/p/headlesseclipse/

Just install the jar in thre dropins dir of Eclipse 3.6 (and also add tptp which is needed for building GlassFish plugin) and
our Hudson job does:
(assuming Eclipse and the added moredules are on /Users/hudson/Desktop/HELIOSRC3)

cd  oepe
echo $JAVA_HOME

rm -rf helios.updatesite/features* helios.updatesite/plugins* helios.updatesite/artifacts.jar* helios.updatesite/content.jar*
/Users/hudson/Desktop/HELIOSRC3/eclipse/Eclipse.app/Contents/MacOS/eclipse -clean -nosplash -data /Users/hudson/workspace/Eclipse\ GlassFish\ Plugin\ for\ OEPE/oepe  -application com.ind.eclipse.headlessworkspace.Application   import  clean build exportupdatesites
cd helios.updatesite
rm -f updatesite.zip*
zip -r updatesite.zip artifacts.jar content.jar features plugins site.xml

